data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!!Nestled on a sprawling 4.07-acre lot is a delightful horse property exuding warmth and charm. The interior is marked by vaulted ceilings and a neutral palette, creating an airy and inviting ambiance. The welcoming living room flows seamlessly into the kitchen, which boasts chocolate-stained cabinets, mosaic tile backsplash, built-in appliances, and stylish pendant lighting. A center island with a breakfast bar serves as the perfect spot for casual dining. The main bedroom is a haven of relaxation, featuring a jetted soaking tub and a private bathroom outfitted with dual sinks, ensuring a tranquil retreat. Complementing the indoor spaces is a cozy AZ room, providing an additional area to unwind and enjoy the serene surroundings. This property is also on a well! The expansive backyard is a blank canvas offering endless possibilities. It has a shed, stalls, and ample space, inviting you to get creative, breathe, and grow. Whether you envision a flourishing garden, a riding arena, or additional equestrian amenities, this property presents the opportunity to bring your dreams to life. Don't miss the chance to make this unique and versatile horse property your own!
